      <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[- Added a `Reverse mouse scroll direction` setting for mouse-wheel scroll actions, with first-run and Settings suggestions for users of tools like LinearMouse, Mos, and UnnaturalScrollWheels while leaving trackpad gestures unchanged.
